## Description {#details}

The resolution for a symbol.

The linker must provide a <a href="/docs/api/structs/llvm/lto/symbolresolution">SymbolResolution</a> for each global symbol based on its internal resolution of that symbol.

Definition at line 546 of file <a href="/docs/api/files/include/include/llvm/include/llvm/lto/lto-h">LTO.h</a>.
